ly for anything is deemed as begging. Basically, the first time is asking, then second and subsequent times are considered begging. The person you are asking will help you if they can or want to the first time. <br><br>2. Kill Stealing<br><br>Whether provoked or not, this is unacceptable. If you have any questions about Kill Stealing, read Verants policy. Basically, all Mobs are fair game, (no one owns a spawn). If the mob is green to you, or someone has engaged the creature already and you take the kill, that is a Kill Steal.<br><br>3. Swearing in public channels<br><br>Anyone saying Sh*t, or F**k, or other words known to be even more vulgar in these channels is unacceptable. OOC, Guild, Say, Shout, Auction. If you are grouped with someone that is offended by your language, and your reported, then that is grounds for removal as well. No exceptions. Basically, make sure you know who your cursing to before you do it.<br><br>Also keep in mind you are playing with people from every possible race, creed, color, ethnic, and personal background.<br><br>4. Harassment of another player<br><br>This includes /shouting, following someone from zone to zone. Continuing to give tells to someone after they make it clear that they do not wish to speak to you. Retaliation is not an excuse. If someone does it to you, use the /ignore command. <br> <p><center><img src="http://silverhawks.freeservers.com/images/fernus.jpg"></center><b><center>Hurrah <a href=http://silverhawks.freeservers.com>Silver Hawks</a>, wherever they may fly! </p></b></center></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub29.ezboard.com/fsilverhawksofdrinalfrm78.showPrevMessage?topicID=4.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub29.ezboard.com/fsilverhawksofdrinalfrm78.showNextMessage?topicID=4.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><